o the following communes:\n\n{|\n|valign=\"top\"|\n*Th\u1ecb tr\u1ea5n \u0110\u1ea7m D\u01a1i\n*Thanh T\u00f9ng\n*Qu\u00e1ch Ph\u1ea9m\n*Qu\u00e1ch Ph\u1ea9m B\u1eafc\n|width=\"45\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n*Tr\u1ea7n Ph\u00e1n\n*T\u00e2n Duy\u1ec7t\n*T\u1ea1 An Kh\u01b0\u01a1ng\n*T\u1ea1 An Kh\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0110\u00f4ng\n|width=\"45\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n*T\u1ea1 An Kh\u01b0\u01a1ng Nam\n*T\u00e2n \u0110\u1ee9c\n*T\u00e2n Ti\u1ebfn\n*Nguy\u1ec5n Hu\u00e2n\n|width=\"45\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n*T\u00e2n Thu\u1eadn\n*Ng\u1ecdc Kh\u00e1nh\n*T\u00e2n Trung\n*T\u00e2n D\u00e2n\n|width=\"45\"|&nbsp;\n|valign=\"top\"|\n|}\n\n== C\u00e0 Mau Bird Sanctuary==\n\u0110\u1ea7m D\u01a1i is famous for the [[C\u00e0 Mau Bird Sanctuary]], which is 45&nbsp;km southeast of [[C\u00e0 Mau]] City. The sanctuary is home to many types of storks. The birds in the preserve tend to make nests in the top of very high trees and search for food in the early mornings.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Districts of Mekong Delta}}\n\n{{coord|8|59|35|N|105|11|38|E|source:kolossus-frwiki|display=title}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Dam Doi District}}\n[[Category:Districts of C\u00e0 Mau Province]]\n{{CaMau-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Alpha Centauri 5932", "label": "safe", "comment": "fix", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C4%90%E1%BA%A7m_D%C6%A1i_District"}
